{"type":"message","id":"a1e83d87","parentId":"b1ea6e29","timestamp":"2026-06-29T15:40:53.809Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the full picture. The bitable has data - it's just that:\n\n1. The most recent entries are from a long time ago (dates show 1772121600000 which is July 2026 - that's weird, this might be a display issue or the data is actually old)\n2. There are also some empty records at the end\n3. The table has 34 total records\n\nThe real problem is:\n- **Sorftime API is broken** (404 errors) - that's why no new products have been added recently\n- The existing data in the table IS there - it's just that new scanning stopped working\n\nSo my previous analysis was correct. The products ARE in the table (there's historical data), but the API is down so no NEW products are coming in.\n\n\nI should clarify for the user that while the API outage is blocking new entries, the existing table data is intact and they've got a solid collection of products across Vietnam and Malaysia, including some strong performers like the S/A-grade items. I'm also noticing some malformed records with empty fields that are cluttering the table.","thinkingSignature":"f7dadb72ad5747a1ac28886041412dae3b41fdb8df4b955d7ccde8d06652a67e"},{"type":"text","text":"表格其实**有数据**，34条记录是有的。我来给你梳理清楚现状：\n\n---\n\n**表格里有什么（按等级）：**\n\n| 等级 | 产品 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 🟢 S级 | 蒜头泡泡抓夹（月销2309/增长180%/毛利66%） | 待采集 |\n| 🟢 A级 | 弹簧夹12件套（月销2899/毛利90%） | 待采集 |\n| 🟢 A级 | 公主蝴蝶结抓夹（月销68036/毛利78%） | 待采集 |\n| 🟢 A级 | 兔子发带（月销5853/毛利96%） | 待采集 |\n| 🟢 A级 | 花朵发夹（月销4000/毛利84%） | 待采集 |\n| 🟡 B级 | MISSHONEY蝴蝶结发圈（月销68089） | 已采集 |\n| 🔴 C/B级 | 多条马来西亚发箍 | 待审批 |\n\n---\n\n**真正的问题：API断了**\n\n数据**已经在表格里**，问题是：\n- **Sorftime API 6/28-29 连续返回404**，新扫描完全停了\n- 所以你说的\"没有新产品进来\"，其实不是表格写不进去——是**根本没扫到新数据**\n\n---\n\n**结论：表格没问题的，是数据源断了。**\n\n你要不要我今天手动重试一次 Sorftime API，确认是否恢复？还是你那边可以直接联系 Sorftime 确认 key 状态？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4607,"output":534,"cacheRead":54868,"cacheWrite":2045,"totalTokens":62054,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782747636079,"responseId":"0691c4f4cc6a8f79f5462f8f470a8ebe","responseModel":"MiniMax-M2.7"}}
