{"type":"message","id":"0408fd60","parentId":"a6df86ed","timestamp":"2026-06-29T15:41:57.076Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The API is working now! Both test 1 (VN without price filter) and test 2 (TH) returned data. The issue was indeed rate limiting - after waiting 3 seconds between requests, the TH query succeeded.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Report back to HALEI that the API is working\n2. The \"暂无相关数据\" from the first test was because the price filter (priceRangeMin:20000 VND ≈ $0.78) was too high for some products, or the nodeId has no results at that price point\n3. Run the actual Vietnam scan without the price filter to get data\n\n\n4. The second test also revealed that nodeId 11046516 for Thailand is outdated - the correct one is 11045697\n\nLet me verify the Vietnam results and execute a proper scan with the correct parameters and appropriate delays between requests.","thinkingSignature":"f1ff30452225c15e5a4c530346ddc0b541c392153385f543896bb1d41333ffa4"},{"type":"text","text":"API **恢复了**！刚才确实是限流——间隔3秒后泰国数据就回来了。让我现在跑一轮越南扫描，不设价格下限：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7y2tnkwa58kg_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer rhblyi…qt09\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"VN\",\"nodeId\":\"11035861\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":50,\"page\":1}},\"id\":4}' \\\n  -w \"\\nHTTP_CODE:%{http_code}\" | grep -v \"^event:\" | head -200"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15737,"output":385,"cacheRead":62199,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78321,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1782747706214,"responseId":"0691c53aad6ce108b6bb84ba4668ad92","r