{"type":"message","id":"b772ee9c","parentId":"777aa4e0","timestamp":"2026-06-29T15:43:01.827Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the issue clearly:\n\n1. **Vietnam nodeId 11035861** returns \"暂无相关数据\" - the nodeId might be wrong or inactive\n2. **Vietnam keyword search \"kẹp tóc\"** returns data but it's returning general merchandise (cosmetics, skincare, etc.) not specifically hair clips\n3. **Thailand nodeId 11045697** returned data successfully\n\nSo the Vietnam nodeId might have changed or become invalid. Let me try a more specific keyword search for Vietnam hair accessories. \n\nActually, looking at the keyword search results for \"kẹp tóc\" (hair clip) - I see products like necklaces, lipstick, etc. \n\nThe search is pulling from multiple categories because \"kẹp tóc\" appears in product names alongside other items. But Thailand's nodeId 11045697 gave me real hair clip results - ProductId 23046546423 with 1346 sales and ProductId 4534004628 with 1183 sales both appear to be legitimate hair clips.\n\nThe Vietnam nodeId 11035861 isn't returning results, so I should try keyword search with \"kẹp tóc\" and filter for products in the hair accessory category. Since v8.0 sends results to HALEI anyway, I'll do a quick scan and report what I find rather than getting bogged down in the details.","thinkingSignature":"5dfad6195637f0c4a3f2642f55913c090bb43db8bb7bb1cf713ae283169b2c5c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n问题找到了：\n\n- **越南 nodeId=11035861** 返回空——这个类目ID可能已变更/失效\n- **越南关键词搜索**能出数据，但搜到的是美妆护肤大类（关键词被泛化了）\n- **泰国 nodeId=11045697** ✅ 完全正常，上一条测试已经拿到了真实发饰数据\n\n**根本原因：越南发饰类目ID失效了。**\n\n我来用关键词补测越南，筛选发饰相关产品：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5ixt42btxr9t_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sleep 5\n# 越南用更精准的关键词，同时限定最低销量\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer rhblyi…qt09\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{