{"type":"message","id":"dc0b1631","parentId":"ca763769","timestamp":"2026-06-29T15:43:37.748Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No output. Let me try a different approach - the keyword search for Vietnam might work differently. Let me check what data we got from the Vietnam keyword search earlier.\n\nActually, the issue might be that the keyword search for Vietnam \"kẹp tóc\" is returning products but not necessarily hair clips - the earlier test showed cosmetics and skincare products. The nodeId approach doesn't work for VN.\n\nLet me take a different approach and just use the Thailand data (which works) to generate some candidates, and report the VN issue to HALEI.\n\nActually, let me try one more time - maybe the issue is that without rate limiting delay the VN results don't come back. \n\nLooking at the test results, Thailand is working fine with good data coming through, but Vietnam with nodeId is completely empty and the keyword search there is pulling in unrelated categories like cosmetics. Since Thailand is functioning properly, I'll focus on that data and flag the Vietnam nodeId problem separately for HALEI to investigate.\n\nThe 6288 pages of results from the Vietnam keyword search confirm there's plenty of data available, but the issue is that \"kẹp tóc\" in the title is matching all kinds of unrelated products. I need to filter more carefully or use the Thailand results as my primary dataset and address the Vietnam categorization issue as a known limitation to report back on. and move forward with what works. Let me summarize the findings and let HALEI know what happened.\n\nThe VN nodeId is broken (returns 0 results), and keyword search is too broad (mixes categories). Thailand works fine. I should report this to HALEI and proceed with Thailand-only scanning while noting the VN issue.\n\nFor now, let me report the current status:\n1. VN nodeId 11035861 is dead (returns empty)\n2. VN keyword search is too broad\n3. TH nodeId 11045697 is working fine\n4. The \"暂无数\" was due to rate limiting + wrong nodeId\n5. I should suggest HALEI find the correct VN nodeId","thinkingSignature":"53b2470e831c300f174125dbacc62c6620000e04e9b8d9a55a3eeb40d2208ee9"},{"type":"text","text":"越南关键词搜索结果混杂（美妆/护肤/食品都在里面），无法单独筛选发饰。让我整理一下现状汇报给你：\n\n---\n\n**诊断结论：**\n\n| 测试项 | 结果 | 原因 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| 越南类目搜索（nodeId=11035861） | ❌ 空 | 类目ID已失效 |\n| 越南关键词搜索（kẹp tóc） | ⚠️ 混杂 | 搜到的多为美妆/护肤，不是发饰 |\n| 泰国类目搜索（nodeId=11045697） | ✅ 正常 | 有真实发饰数据 |\n\n---\n\n**根本原因：**\n\n1. **限流**：你猜对了——之前请求太密，被短暂封了，间隔3秒后恢复\n2. **越南类目ID挂了**：11035861 这个 Shopee 越南发饰类目ID现在返回空值，可能Shopee侧类目结构变了\n3. **泰国正常**：nodeId 11045697 完全能用\n\n---\n\n**需要你决定：**\n\n1. 越南新类目ID需要从 Shopee 越南站重新确认（可以试 `shopee_category_search_from_name` 工具查）\n2. 目前泰国数据正常，可以继续跑泰国选品\n3. 越南站点需要你帮我找到正确的 nodeId 才能继续\n\n你想先修越南的类目ID，还是先用泰国数据跑起来？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":32510,"output":718,"cacheRead":62199,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95427,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782747794974,"responseId":"0691c593bc2b6c406fc3fd8d0687648c","responseModel":"MiniMax-M2.7"}}
